data.description: Move in ready ,enjoy the privacy of this ranch home. As soon as you pull into the driveway you will get a sense of serenity. This home is Generously set back off of the roadway. More than meets the eye! Take a look inside! Enjoy one level living with an open floor plan that offers a large living room/great room, oversized dining room, eat in kitchen, 3 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom. Recent improvements include new laminate flooring in common area of home, new wall to wall carpet, new counter tops installed and new appliances are here! Well maintained mechanically including furance ,water heater, well pump, roof, windows , siding , Exterior has fresh stone base in driveway, property for lush lawn. There are more upgrades throughout the home! Come take a look!
